OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBecoming
OL,6,Frather cloudy during the evening,
OL,7,Fwhich might lead to the odd spot of
OL,8,Frain or drizzle over the western hills
OL,9,Flater in the night. Warmer than the
OL,10,Fprevious night and feeling humid too.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FBecoming increasingly cloudy
OL,13,Fthrough the day, with patches of light
OL,14,Frain moving in from the west. Rain
OL,15,Fpossibly turning more showery in the
OL,16,Fevening. Warm and humid conditions
OL,17,Fthroughout.
